# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9.9-eclipse-temurin-21-alpine AS builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .

RUN mvn dependency:go-offline -B --no-transfer-progress

COPY . .

RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests -B --no-transfer-progress && \
    mv target/*.jar /app.jar

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

RUN apk update && \
    apk add --no-cache curl fontconfig ttf-dejavu && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

RUN apk add --no-cache openjdk-17-jre-base openssl

RUN keytool -importcert -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt \
        -alias aws-rds-ca -file <(openssl s_client -connect rds.amazonaws.com:443 -servername rds.amazonaws.com 2>/dev/null | openssl x509) && \
    keytool -importcert -keystore $JAVA_HOME/lib/security/cacerts -storepass changeit -noprompt \
        -alias azure-digicert-root -file <(curl -s https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt)

RUN addgroup -g 1001 -S app && \
    adduser -u 1001 -S -G app app

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder --chown=app:app /app.jar /app/app.jar

LABEL maintainer="your-email@example.com" \
      version="1.0.0" \
      description="Java analytics dashboard"

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

USER app

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
